Thats means you have been playing around with you enviourment varaibles,
make sure you have this in one path:

%SystemRoot%\system32;%SystemRoot%;%SystemRoot%\System32\Wbem;C:\Program Files\Acer\Empowering Technology\eDataSecurity\;C:\Program Files\Acer\Empowering Technology\eDataSecurity\x86;C:\Program Files\Acer\Empowering Technology\eDataSecurity\x64;C:\Program Files\Quic

It may not be the same depending on your computer.
